name: Virevoh
description: The Virevoh is an unstoppable force of lightning, soaring through the streets like a streak of white-hot energy. With its powerful cyber-enhancements, this sedan is capable of powering through the toughest races, reaching speeds that could rival even the swiftest of rivals. Its superior handling and lightning-quick reactions make it a cyberpunk's favorite in the race-track, leaving the competition stunned in its wake.
